<L>__{exterior ridgemont mall night}
<A>__{kids are pouring into the ridgemont mall. summer banners are already up.}
<L>__{interior the mall night}
<A>__{in the midst of all the kids and shoppers, we see the rat walking slowly down the promenade. he is wearing an army surplus jacket, and his hands are buried deep in his pockets. two girls pass his way. one smiles briefly at him, and the rat turns to watch her pass. he is about to say something to her, then no. he walks on, sees swenson's ice cream parlor up ahead. the rat decides to walk the other way.}
